Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:48.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. Today, I'm a new man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.99,0:01:51.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me fix that for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:52.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:55.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to look cooler, huh? How sickening...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.21,0:01:58.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, my popularity is only going to increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:01.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you'll be buying those new shoes for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:02.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:06.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly changing your hairstyle won't make you popular. you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:09.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for you. What good will it do to start wearing red lipstick all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.85,0:02:15.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,An opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:23.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan! Chiharu-chan! Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:28.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do now. darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:29.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.01,0:02:31.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Th...{\alpha&HFF&}This feels totally awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.70,0:02:33.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Th...This feels totally awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:34.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That goes for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:39.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you walking with us anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:40.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There's some stuff I have to do at Nakao's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:44.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you ruined my perfectly styled hair after it took so long it almost made me late for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.38,0:02:46.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still going on about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:48.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only are you small in body, you're small in character too.{I think she meant by character is his penis or balls}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:50.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna sue you for defamation!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:51.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead anytime,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:53.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Nakao. let's go get our fortunes told!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:55.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunes?
