Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:03.24,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\c&HFBFEFB&\3c&HAE98D9&\pos(358,169)}Couple Compatibility
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:03.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Our compatibility is 85% !
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:05.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiharu-chan, Suzuki. You guys should have a go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.47,0:03:10.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, give it a go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:27.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You pick Nobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:33.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Otani, want to go see Umibouzu's live concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:37.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of mine got two extra tickets and asked me to find people to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:42.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Umibouzu?! Seriously? I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You like him too, Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:47.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! l love him! He's just awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:49.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's totally awesome, isn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard his new song?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:53.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I have! it's freaking awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:55.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,it's great! His voice is just amazing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Totally, totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:58.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you two try going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:00.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:02.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:04.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to share the same interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:06.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Your compatibility must be pretty high.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:08.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we compatible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:10.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You both like Umibouzu, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:12.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That just happens to be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.36,0:04:15.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A Girl shouldn't say a thing like "balls-balls".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:15.80,lovely - TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}The expression "Tama-tama" means "happens to be the case" but the word "tama" itself is a slang term for "balls".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:17.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I did NOT say "balls"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:20.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I hate girls like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:22.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to hear that from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:25.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... excuse me, are you ready to order?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:27.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sure. Just a second...
