Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:35.12,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\c&H5B5BC5&\3c&H60597C&\frz14\blur.5\pos(509,405)}Hawaiian Dancer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:32.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! A new item on the menu..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:34.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:37.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,One Hawaiian Dancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:40.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:44.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:49.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be in love!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:52.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Like l said. you should just go for Otani-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:53.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Chiharu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:54.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:56.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I have to go for that midget?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:59.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I need someone who is at least taller than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:01.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But Otani-Kun is pretty popular, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:04.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pulling my leg again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:07.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go watch the basketball team practice after school, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:20.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Look Those girls are probably from second or third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:23.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He got the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:27.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,They always get worked up watching Otani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:29.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:36.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... the midget is actually pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:40.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. That's quite a jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:42.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:46.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go for a jump shot just to look cool when you're so short.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:48.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the coach so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:49.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He got it in didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:50.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:53.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about your height before you jump, shorty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:56.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?! What an irritating old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:57.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:05:59.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:06.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani got chewed out by the coach...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:06.54,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Awww...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:08.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:07.86,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:10.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He is so--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.42,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:14.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So the midget had this up his sleeve too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:15.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How underhanded!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:22.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that ugly face?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:24.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:27.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're using itty-bitty flower hair clips to make yourself look cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I borrowed these from my older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:32.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:34.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like a little girl, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:38.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:40.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:42.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'll buy you shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:46.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,When the time comes, you'll be the one buying me tons of games!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:46.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:50.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What was she on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:53.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to do something, otherwise..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:55.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:57.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:06:58.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-Chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:06:59.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hook up parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:00.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any hook up parties coming up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:01.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:03.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hook up parties?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:06.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:09.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to surprise him and find a great guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:10.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:12.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:15.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A horse...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:17.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A monkey..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A bird...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:20.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:23.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...and a pig?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:25.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, a zoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:34.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, zoos aren't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:36.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoos are fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a giraffe too, after all, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:42.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. It's fine. This is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:44.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's important is what's on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:47.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Koizumi-Chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:52.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What's wrong? what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:54.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling down?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:07:59.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, how tall are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:03.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It came over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,170 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:08.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're really tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.95,0:08:13.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're this tall now, you may even crack three meters by the time you graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:15.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:18.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How could that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:20.47,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that funny? That was funny, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:22.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,People always say I'm funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:25.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:29.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It always comes to this in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:37.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how'd it go yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:39.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell from the expression on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:41.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because your standards are too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:42.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:46.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go around saying {\i1}"your standards are too high"{\i0}  to people who don't have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:49.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked me what kind of guys I like, and I gave you a list of qualities...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:53.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't seriously expect to meet a guy that has all of them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:58.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Maybe my standards are too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:08:59.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:00.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:01.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,As a person...{\alpha&HFF&}as a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:02.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,As a person... as a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...It's no good to go on like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:06.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:11.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I'm just no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:13.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that, this. Very bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:21.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! My Umibouzu ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got it from Nakao.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:25.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for Umibouzu's Christmas Live concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:26.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:30.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,December 25th Lover's day, Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:30.08,lovely - TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}In Japan, Christmas is a holiday for couples and lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:33.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:37.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to do something as miserable as spend Christmas with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:38.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:40.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to throw those same words back in your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:41.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:45.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohh... {\alpha&HFF&}Why has it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:46.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohh...Why has it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:47.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...turned out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:51.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What country are you supposed to be from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:53.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with the two of you going together, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:53.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:58.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I have to walk around on Christmas being called All Hanshin-Kyoujin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:01.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the Christmas atmosphere will help love flow between you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:04.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If an amazon like her gets swept up in any kind of flow, she'll probably clog the drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's flowing where now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:20.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we do walk along a romantic Christmas street together,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:22.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no way that love will develop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:26.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sneeze like an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:28.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I caught a cold recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you seriously looking for a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:34.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am. Our challenge isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:38.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you've got no plans for Christmas anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:41.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:46.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just go to the concert and then go straight home, before any romantic feelings develop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:53.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether we take our time getting there, or take longer going home, it's not like we'll fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:55.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:59.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what kind of girls do you like, Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:00.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:04.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not the type who sneezes like an old man, at the very least.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:08.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,When a girl sneezes, she should cover her mouth with her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:10.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,See, like tha...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:20.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiharu-chan with different colored hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:21.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:22.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But... {\alpha&HFF&}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:23.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:26.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! There are two Chiharu-Chans?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:28.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:30.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsushi-Kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:38.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:44.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:45.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsushi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:51.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsushi-kun? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:52.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:55.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:56.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:58.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:11:59.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur7}Th... {\alpha&HFF&}This is a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.16,0:12:02.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur7}Th... This is a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur7}This girl looks exactly like Chiharu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:09.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I'm kind of in a hurry, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:09.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:21.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Atsushi-kun, who was that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,None of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:27.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Atsushi-kun? You can tell me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:29.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How suspicious, how suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:31.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She used to be my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:42.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Used to be"{\i0}... You mean she's your ex-girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:44.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so surprised?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:46.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I lie to you about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:51.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you wouldn't. You are Otani, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:52.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:56.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been alive for like 15, 16 odd years, It's only normal to have dated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:57.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:59.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not something to be proud of!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:03.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:05.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate shock...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:11.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,An ex-girlfriend... That Otani's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:13.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So even someone like Otani... How ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:16.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I heard about it from Nakao-chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:19.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl, Kanzaki Mayu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:24.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,was the manager of the basketball club back when they were in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:27.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She went out with Otani-kun for two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:32.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And apparently Otani-kun really liked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:32.43,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,So it really is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:46.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd always thought that Otani had never dated anyone since the day he was born, like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:48.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I feel like I've been left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:52.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Otani, why did you break up with your ex?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:54.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you asking about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I can't imagine why you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:59.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually managed to get a girlfriend, but then broke up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:04.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't break up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:06.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She dumped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:07.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:09.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:12.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She suddenly told me that there was another guy she liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:17.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It was particularly depressing because the guy she liked...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:20.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...was over two meters tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.43,0:14:22.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We used to call him the Equestrian Ground Giant of Nishi Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:26.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was probably because of my height.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:30.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I'm sure that was just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:32.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she didn't pick him just for his height.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:32.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it was a coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:35.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,... I was already conscious about my height.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:38.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm even more so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:47.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I said a thing like that, you'd punch me again, right Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:51.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:59.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, So Otani has a past like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:02.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:05.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You will find happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:12.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:16.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I completely understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:18.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting dumped over something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:20.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you're so concerned about height.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:22.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:24.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to live on, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:35.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I left my purse at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:37.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys go on ahead, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:38.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:55.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So we've decide to have a party with everyone who was in the basketball club on the 25th.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:57.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if you could spare some time on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:15:59.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:02.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The more you look, the more she looks like Chiharu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:05.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that she looks like Chiharu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:08.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiharu-chan looks like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:12.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why he liked Chiharu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:15.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to come, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:17.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:17.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:17.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:30.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? What's with that conflicted look?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:32.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be Otani...{\alpha&HFF&}still likes that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:35.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be Otani... still likes that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:39.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the 25th...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:40.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:43.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to the Umibouzu concert by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:45.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ko-Koizumi when did you-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:46.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Something she wants to say, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:49.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be that she wants to get back together...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:53.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't go, and don't end up getting back together you might blame it on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:55.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:59.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than finding a new girlfriend, why not get back with your old one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:01.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a faster way to settle our challenge too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:03.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:07.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, but since I helped you a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:09.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...we'll cancel the shoes thing, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:10.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just treat you to tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:11.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Materialistic, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:13.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:17.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know whether to consider you a good or bad person, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a good person, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:28.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But, to see you show an expression like that... It surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan, Chiharu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:35.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And so it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:36.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean {\i1}"and so it is"{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:39.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be all alone for Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:41.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to hang out for a bit before the Concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:44.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:51.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... if that's impossible, hanging out on Christmas eve is okay too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:56.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'll be going over to my darling's place on the 24th for an overnight Christmas party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:02.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to give Suzuki-kun a scarf on the 25th, but I haven't finished it yet, so on the 24th...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:05.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, but if I get working on it right away, I might have time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:10.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. It's fine. You don't need to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:12.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ok We're still friends, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:13.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:17.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Christmas has nothing to do with us Japanese anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:19.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it matter if I'm alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:32.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so bored, I came way too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:36.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:41.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! My stockings ripped! I'm bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:51.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else must be having fun right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:55.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani must have made up with his ex-girlfriend too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:19:00.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? I've been left all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:05.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Otani has a girlfriend, he probably won't hang out with me anymore either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:07.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:13.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's winter vacation, but even if I want to hang out with everybody, I'll just be in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:15.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,My leg hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The concert's about to start too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:22.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it matter if I see Umibouzu? What does it matter if I get excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:25.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like there's anyone I can share that excitement with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:30.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes down to it... {\alpha&HFF&} I feel really lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:31.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes down to it.... I feel really lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:34.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:35.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:38.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounded like Otani's voice just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:43.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:46.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:46.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:48.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:50.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? We're going to the Umibouzu concert, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:55.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But what about your ex-girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:19:58.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She can wait till next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:02.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I did make plans with you first, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:08.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have hesitated a bit, but it's not like I'd break a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.44,0:20:11.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to owe you any favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:12.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:13.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
