Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:36.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Kne...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:37.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Kne?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:38.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Kne...{\alpha&HFF&}Kne... K-Kne...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.41,0:20:40.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Kne... Kne...{\alpha&HFF&}K-Kne...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:40.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Kne... Kne...K-Kne...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:42.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you? A bird, now?
